texts.content: {"text":"2. Bu kitobning nozil qilinishi aziyzu o`ta ilmli \nAlloh tomonidandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,70]}]}

{"text":"3. U, gunohni mag`firat qilguvchi, 
tavbani qabul etguvchi, iqobi shiddatli 
va fazlu karam sohibi bo`lgan Zotdir. 
Undan o`zga ibodatga sazovor zot yo`q. 
Qaytish Uning O`zigaginadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,184]}]}

{"text":"4. Allohning oyatlari haqida faqatgina 
kufr keltirganlar talashib-tortishurlar. 
Bas, ularning yurtlarda aylanib yurishlari 
seni aldab qo`ymasin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,147]}]}

{"text":"5. Ulardan oldin Nuh qavmi va ular ketidan 
kelgan firqalar ham yolg`onchi qilgan edilar. 
Har ummat o`z Payg`ambarini tutishga qasd qildi 
va haqni yo`qotish uchun botil ila mujodala etdi. 
Bas, Men ularni tutdim. 
Bas, Mening iqobim qanday bo`ldi!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,249]}]}

{"text":"6. Kufr keltirganlarga ham Robbingning \n(azob) so`zi xuddi ana shunday haq bo`ldi. \nAlbatta, ular do`zax egalaridir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,116]}]}

{"text":"7. Arshni ko`tarib turganlar va uning \natrofidagilar Robbilariga hamd ila tasbih ayturlar, Unga iymon keltirurlar ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,114]}]}

{"text":"va iymon keltirganlarga mag`firat so`rab: \nEy Robbimiz, rahmating va ilming ila har bir narsani qurshagansan, bas, tavba qilib, yo`lingga ergashganlarni mag`firat qilgin va ularni do`zax azobidan saqlagin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,206]}]}

{"text":"8. Ey Robbimiz, ularni ham, otalaridan, juftlaridan \nva zurriyotlaridan ahli solih bo`lganlarini ham \nO`zing ularga va'da qilgan adn jannatlariga kiritgin. Albatta, Sening O`zing aziyzu o`ta hikmatli zotsan.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,207]}]}

{"text":"9. Va ularni yomonliklardan saqla, o`sha kuni kimni yomonliklardan saqlasang, batahqiq, unga rahim qilibsan. Ana o`sha buyuk yutuqdir, (derlar).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,145]}]}

{"text":"10. Albatta, kufr keltirganlarga: Iymonga chaqirilganingizda kufr keltirgan chog`ingizdagi Allohning g`azabi sizning o`zingizga (hozirgi) \ng`azabingizdan kattaroqdir, deb nido qilinur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,186]}]}

{"text":"11. Ular: Ey Robbimiz, \nSen bizni ikki marta o`ldirding, ikki marta tiriltirding. Bas, biz gunohlarimizni e'tirof etdik. \nEndi chiqishning biron yo`li bormi?  dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,170]}]}

{"text":"12. Bunday bo`lishingiz Allohning yolg`iz O`ziga da'vat qilinganida, kufr keltirganingiz, Unga shirk keltirilsa, iymon keltirganingiz uchundir. \nBas, hukm oliy va ulug` Allohnikidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,182]}]}

{"text":"13. Uning O`zi sizga oyat (belgi)larini ko`rsatadigan, osmondan sizga rizq tushiradigan Zotdir. \nFaqat qaytadigan kishigina anglar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,131]}]}

{"text":"14. Bas, agar kofirlar yoqtirmasalar ham, \nAllohga dinni xolis qilgan holingizda yolvoring.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,91]}]}

{"text":"15. U, darajasi yuksak, Arsh egasi bo`lgan Zotdir. \nU, O`z amri ila bandalaridan kimni xohlasa, o`shanga muloqot kunidan ogohlantirishi uchun ruhni tushirur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,157]}]}

{"text":"16. O`sha kunda ular zohir bo`lurlar. 
Allohga ulardan biron narsa maxfiy qolmas. 
Bugun mulk kimnikidir?! 
Yakkayu yolg`iz, Qahhor Allohnikidir!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,145]}]}

{"text":"17. Bugungi kunda har bir jon o`zi qilgan kasbga yarasha jazo olur. Bugunga kunda zulm yo`qdur. Albatta, Alloh hisobni tez qilguvchi Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"18. Sen ularni yaqinlashguvchi Kundan ogohlantir. \nO`shanda jonlar xalqumga kelib, g`am-g`ussaga \nto`lib turarlar. Zolimlar uchun hech bir do`st ham, itoat qilinadigan shafoatchi ham yo`q.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,188]}]}

{"text":"19. U zot ko`zlarning xiyonatini ham, \ndillar maxfiy tutgan narsalarni ham bilur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"20. Alloh haq ila hukm qilur. \nUndan o`zga iltijo qilayotganlari esa, hech narsa bilan hukm qilmaslar. Albatta, Allohning O`zi o`ta eshitguvchi va o`ta ko`rguvchi Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,170]}]}

{"text":"21. Axir, ular yer yuzida yurib, \no`zlaridan oldin o`tganlarning oqibati qanday \nbo`lganiga nazar solmaydilarmi?! ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,114]}]}

{"text":"Holbuki, o`shalar ulardan ko`ra quvvatliroq va 
yer yuzida asarlari ko`proq bo`lgan edilar. 
Bas, Alloh o`shalarni gunohlari sababli tutdi. 
Ularga Allohdan o`zga bir saqlovchi bo`lmadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,186]}]}

{"text":"22. Bunday bo`lishining sababi shuki, \nularga Payg`ambarlari aniq hujjatlar bilan kelar edilar, ular esa, kufr keltirdilar. Bas, Alloh ularni tutdi. Albatta, U kuchli va iqobi shiddatli Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,193]}]}

{"text":"23. Batahqiq, \nBiz Musoni O`z oyatlarimiz va ochiq hujjat ila yubordik:","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,71]}]}

{"text":"24. Fir'avnga, Homonga va Qorunga. \nBas, ular: (Bu) sehrgar va kazzob, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"25. Muso ularga Bizning huzurimizdan haq ila 
kelgan chog`da, ular: U bilan birga iymon keltirganlarning o`g`illarini qatl qilinglar, 
qizlarini tirik qoldiringlar, dedilar. Kofirlarning 
makr-hiylasi zalolatdan boshqa narsa emas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,232]}]}

{"text":"26. Fir'avn: Meni qo`yinglar, Musoni o`ldiray. \nMayli, Robbiga duo qilsin. Albatta, men uning diningizni almashtirishidan va yer yuzida fasod chiqarishidan qo`rqmoqdaman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,178]}]}

{"text":"27. Muso: Albatta, men Robbim va Robbingiz bo`lgan Zotdan hisob kuniga iymon keltirmaydigan har bir mutakabbirdan panoh so`rayman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,138]}]}

{"text":"28. Fir'avn ahlidan bo`lgan, iymonini berkitib yuradigan bir mo`min kishi: Bir odamni, \nAlloh Robbimdir, degani uchun o`ldirasizlarmi?! Holbuki, u sizga Robbingizdan ochiq-oydin \nhujjatlar ila kelmishdir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,206]}]}

{"text":"Agar u yolg`onchi bo`lsa, yolg`oni o`ziga zarar. \nAgar rostgo`y bo`lsa, unda u va'da qilayotgan ba'zi musiybatlar sizga yetar. Albatta, Alloh isrofchi va kazzob bo`lgan shaxsni hidoyat qilmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,192]}]}

{"text":"29. Ey qavmim, bugungi kunda mulk siznikidir. 
Yer yuzida yuzaga chiqib turibsizlar. 
Agar bizga Allohning azobi kelsa, 
unda bizga kim yordam berar?!  dedi. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,160]}]}

{"text":"Fir'avn: Men sizga o`zim ko`rayotgan narsadan boshqani ko`rsatmasman va sizlarni to`g`ri yo`ldan boshqaga yo`llamasman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,127]}]}

{"text":"30. Iymon keltirgan kishi: Ey qavmim, albatta, \nmen sizga ham boshqa firqalar kuniga o`xshash kun...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,101]}]}

{"text":"31. Nuh qavmi, Od, Samud va ulardan keyingilar \nholiga o`xshash hol bo`lishidan qo`rqurman. \nAlloh bandalarga zulmni iroda qilmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,130]}]}

{"text":"32. Ey qavmim, albatta, men sizlarga nidolashuv kunidan qo`rqurman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,67]}]}

{"text":"33. U kunda ortga qarab qochursiz. \nSiz uchun Allohdan hech bir qutqarguvchi bo`lmas. Kimni Alloh zalolatga ketkazsa, bas, unga hech bir hidoyatchi bo`lmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,156]}]}

{"text":"34. Batahqiq, bundan oldin Yusuf ochiq-oydin hujjatlar ila keldi. Bas, siz u o`zingizga keltirgan narsaga shak keltirib, turib oldingiz. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,137]}]}

{"text":"Nihoyat, u vafot etgan paytda: \nAlloh undan keyin Payg`ambar yubormas, dedingiz. Alloh shunday qilib, isrofchi va shubhachi bo`lgan kimsani zalolatga ketkazdi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,161]}]}

{"text":"35. Allohning oyatlari haqida o`zlariga kelgan 
hujjat-dalilsiz talashib-tortishadiganlar 
Alloh tomonidan ham, iymon keltirganlar tomonidan ham qattiq g`azabga qolurlar. Alloh shunday qilib, 
har bir mutakabbir va zo`ravon qalbni muhrlar, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,246]}]}

{"text":"36. Fir'avn dedi: Ey, Homon, menga bir baland \nqasr bino qil, shoyad, sabablarga yetsam.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,89]}]}

{"text":"37. Osmonlarning sabablariga yetsam, 
so`ngra Musoning Ilohiga boqsam. Albatta, men uni yolg`onchi deb, gumon qilmoqdaman. 
Shunday qilib, Fir'avnga uning yomon amali ziynatlandi va u yo`ldan to`sildi. Fir'avnning 
makr-hiylasi ziyonkorlikdan boshqa narsa emas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,262]}]}

{"text":"38. Iymon keltirgan kishi: Ey qavmim, menga ergashinglar, sizni to`g`ri yo`lga hidoyat qilurman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,97]}]}

{"text":"39. Ey qavmim, \nbu dunyo hayoti vaqtinchalik bir matoh, xolos. Albatta, oxirat, o`shaning o`zi barqarorlik diyoridir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,117]}]}

{"text":"40. Kim biror yomonlik qilsa, faqat o`shanga yarasha jazo oladi, xolos. Erkakdir, ayoldir, har kim mo`min \nbo`lgan holida solih amal qilsa, bas, ana o`shalar jannatga kirurlar, u yerda hisobsiz rizqlanurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,207]}]}

{"text":"41. Ey qavmim, nechun men sizni najotga chaqirsam, siz meni do`zaxga chaqirursiz?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,82]}]}

{"text":"42. Siz meni Allohga kufr keltirishimga va \no`zim bilmagan narsani Unga shirk keltirishimga chaqirmoqdasiz. Holbuki, men sizni aziyzu o`ta \nmag`firatli Zotga chaqirmoqdaman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,173]}]}

{"text":"43. Hech shubha yo`qki, albatta, siz meni chaqirayotgan narsaning dunyoda ham, 
oxiratda ham da'vatga haqqi yo`qdir. 
Albatta, qaytib borarimiz Allohgadir. 
Albatta, isrofchilar, ayni o`shalar do`zax egalaridir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,211]}]}

{"text":"44. Hali, men sizga aytayotgan gaplarni eslaysizlar. Men ishimni Allohning O`ziga topshirdim. Albatta, Alloh bandalarini aniq ko`rib turguvchidir, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,153]}]}

{"text":"45. Bas, Alloh uni makrlari yomonliklaridan saqladi \nva Fir'avn ahlini yomon azob o`rab oldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,93]}]}

{"text":"46. U olovdir. Unga ertayu kech ko`ndalang qilinurlar. Soat (qiyomat) qoim bo`lganida esa: \nFir'avn ahlini eng ashaddiy azobga kiritinglar, deyilur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,150]}]}

{"text":"47. O`shanda ular do`zaxda bir-birlari ila xusumat qilurlar. Bas, zaiflar mutakabbirlik qilganlarga: 
Albatta, biz sizga ergashuvchi bo`lgan edik. 
Endi siz bizning do`zax nasibamizdan biror 
bo`lagini daf' qilasizlarmi?!  derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,233]}]}

{"text":"48. Mutakabbirlik qilganlar: Albatta hammamiz uning ichidamiz. Shubhasiz, Alloh bandalar orasida hukm chiqarib bo`ldi, derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,128]}]}

{"text":"49. Do`zaxda turganlar jahannam qo`riqchilariga: \nRobbingizga duo qilinglar, bizdan biror kun azobni yengillatsin, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,125]}]}

{"text":"50. Ular: Sizga Payg`ambarlaringiz ochiq-oydin hujjatlar bilan kelmagan edilarmi?!  dedilar. \nBular: Ha, deyishdi. Ular: Bas, duo qilaveringlar. Kofirlarning duosi zalolatdan boshqa narsa emas, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,209]}]}

{"text":"51. Albatta, Biz Payg`ambarlarimizga va iymon keltirganlarga bu dunyo hayotida va guvohlar turgan kunda ham nusrat berurmiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,124]}]}

{"text":"52.
